name: No Looking Back
description: Leah gets the results of Ali’s brain MRI and is relieved to find out there’s nothing wrong with her brain. Jenelle is spending time with Jace and finally at peace with her mom, but Kieffer calls and she agrees to take him to turn himself in for the domestic charges she filed against him. Kailyn and Jordan are having sex so she decides to try a new form of birth control, but struggles to have an adult conversation with Jordan about it. The day after her knee surgery Chelsea and Adam get into a fight and he storms off with Aubree, leaving Chelsea to fend for herself.
